{
  "texts": [
    "Many concerns about the risks and harms of bias in AI have been motivating the fast growing multidisciplinary research on fair-AI.",
    "First, we have concisely summarized topics in policies and best practices, thus providing to researchers and practitioners pointers to inventories, guidelines and survey papers.",
    "On the one side of the spectrum of possible actions to prevent those risks and harms, there is the option not to use AI.",
    "On the other side of the spectrum, there is the option to address the origins of AI harms at societal level.",
    "In between the two options, there are methods for documenting bias, techniques for mitigating bias, and approaches for auditing AI systems."
  ]
}